---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Frequently Asked Questions"
  description="Common questions about football assessment services, online calls, payments and cancellations."
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQs -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq">
          <summary class="faq__question">What services do you offer?</summary>
          <div class="faq__answer">
            <p>
              I offer one-to-one online calls focused on football development,
              performance analysis and coaching support. These calls can include:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Reviewing match or training footage</li>
              <li>Technical, tactical or positional guidance</li>
              <li>Identifying strengths and areas for improvement</li>
              <li>Discussing your football pathway or development plan</li>
              <li>Support for parents on understanding the football environment</li>
              <li>Coaching ideas, session design or age-group development</li>
              <li>Planning next steps in your football journey</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              Whether you're a player, parent, coach or someone wanting clarity,
              each call is tailored to your needs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq">
          <summary class="faq__question">Which platforms can I use for my online call?</summary>
          <div class="faq__answer">
            <p>You can select the platform that works best for you:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Zoom</strong> — standard option for most countries</li>
              <li><strong>VooV Meeting (Tencent Meeting)</strong> — recommended for users in mainland China as it is reliable and fully accessible</li>
              <li><strong>Microsoft Teams</strong> — ideal if you prefer an alternative to Zoom</li>
              <li><strong>Mobile call</strong> — perfect if you'd rather talk by phone or have low internet access</li>
            </ul>
            <p>You'll be able to choose your preferred method when booking.</p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq">
          <summary class="faq__question">How long does an online call last?</summary>
          <div class="faq__answer">
            <p>
              Each online call typically lasts 60 minutes. If the call type is
              different (e.g. introduction or short analysis), the exact duration
              will be shown at booking. I'm also flexible — calls can be longer
              or shorter if required.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq">
          <summary class="faq__question">Why are prices different in each country?</summary>
          <div class="faq__answer">
            <p>
              Prices vary slightly by country to keep the service fair and
              accessible. Factors that influence pricing include:
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Local taxes and digital service fees</li>
              <li>Currency conversion rates</li>
              <li>Regional payment processing charges</li>
              <li>Cost-of-living differences and economic conditions</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              These adjustments help ensure the same quality of support globally
              while keeping pricing balanced.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq">
          <summary class="faq__question">Can I join from China or other restricted regions?</summary>
          <div class="faq__answer">
            <p>Yes. Clients in mainland China are very welcome.</p>
            <p>
              Because some international platforms face internet restrictions, I
              offer alternatives such as VooV Meeting, Microsoft Teams and mobile
              calls. Simply choose the option that works best for your connection.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq">
          <summary class="faq__question">What is your cancellation policy?</summary>
          <div class="faq__answer">
            <p>
              You may cancel or reschedule up to 24 hours before your call.
              Last-minute cancellations may still be charged, as the time is set
              aside specifically for you.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq">
          <summary class="faq__question">What happens if I'm late to the call?</summary>
          <div class="faq__answer">
            <p>
              If you join late, the call will still finish at the scheduled time
              to avoid overlap with other bookings. I recommend joining a couple
              of minutes early so you can settle in comfortably.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq">
          <summary class="faq__question">How do I pay?</summary>
          <div class="faq__answer">
            <p>
              All payments are taken securely through the website at the time of
              booking. Prices will display in your local currency where possible.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq">
          <summary class="faq__question">Who are online calls suitable for?</summary>
          <div class="faq__answer">
            <p>Online calls are suitable for:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Players wanting development feedback</li>
              <li>Parents seeking guidance or clarity</li>
              <li>Coaches looking for ideas or support</li>
              <li>Anyone with football-related questions</li>
              <li>Individuals wanting to talk through performance, progression or next steps</li>
            </ul>
            <p>
              There is no long-term commitment — you can book whenever you feel
              it's helpful.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-contact">
        <p>
          If you have any questions, I'm happy to help:
          <a href="mailto:michael@mulhernfc.com">michael@mulhernfc.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem 2rem;
    background-color: var(--color-off-white);
  }

  .faq-list {
    max-width: 740px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .faq {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-grey-200);
  }

  .faq__question {
    display: block;
    padding: 1.25rem 2rem 1.25rem 0;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-navy);
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .faq__question::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq__question::after {
    content: '+';
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-grey-400);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .faq[open] .faq__question::after {
    content: '\2212';
  }

  .faq__answer {
    padding: 0 0 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-grey-600);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .faq__answer p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .faq__answer p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .faq__answer ul {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .faq__answer li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
  }

  .faq__answer li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.6em;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .faq-contact {
    max-width: 740px;
    margin: 2.5rem auto 0;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-grey-600);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  .faq-contact a {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .faq-contact a:hover {
    color: var(--color-gold-hover);
  }
</style>
